plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: Checked-Out Objects by Type
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: User query to find Checked-Out objects by type.

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM WorkspaceObject WHERE "object_name" = "${object_name = }" AND "sr5ObjectTypeReduced" = "${sr5ObjectTypeReduced = }" AND "owning_user.user_id" = "${CheckedOutbyUser = }" AND "creation_date" >= "${CheckedOutAfter = }" AND "creation_date" <= "${CheckedOutBefore = }"
